headline: Visa Announces the General Availability of Visa AR Manager in the U.S.
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, May 21, 2025--Visa (NYSE:V), a global leader in digital payments, announced the general availability of its innovative product, Visa AR Manager, in the United States. Visa AR Manager is designed to grow and maintain existing card volume by automating the virtual card transaction process, addressing a significant pain point for suppliers accepting commercial credentials.
